{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"IronUI"}],"title":"Accessibility"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/ironui\/accessibility"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Build inclusive interfaces with IronUI’s accessibility features."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI\/Theming"],"anchor":"Essentials","generated":true}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI is built with accessibility as a core principle. Every component supports VoiceOver, Dynamic Type, and reduced motion preferences out of the box."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"VoiceOver Support","anchor":"VoiceOver-Support"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All IronUI components provide meaningful accessibility labels and traits."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Automatic Labeling","anchor":"Automatic-Labeling"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components automatically generate appropriate labels:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Automatically announces \"Primary button, Submit\"","IronButton(\"Submit\", variant: .filled) { }","","\/\/ Announces \"Toggle, Enable notifications, On\"","IronToggle(\"Enable notifications\", isOn: $isEnabled)","","\/\/ Announces \"Avatar for John Doe, Online\"","IronAvatar(name: \"John Doe\", status: .online)"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Custom-Labels","text":"Custom Labels"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override default labels when needed:"}]},{"code":["IronButton(\"\", variant: .filled, leadingIcon: \"plus\") { }","    .accessibilityLabel(\"Add new item\")","","IronIcon(systemName: \"star.fill\", color: .warning)","    .accessibilityLabel(\"Favorite\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Composite-Elements","text":"Composite Elements"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI combines related elements for efficient VoiceOver navigation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Chip with icon + label + dismiss = single VoiceOver element","IronChip(\"Swift\", icon: \"swift\") {","    \/\/ dismiss action","}","\/\/ Announces: \"Swift, Removable, Button. Actions available: Remove\""]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Dynamic-Type","text":"Dynamic Type"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI scales appropriately with the user’s preferred text size."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Automatic-Scaling","level":3,"text":"Automatic Scaling"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All text and text-related measurements scale with Dynamic Type:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Text automatically scales","IronText(\"Welcome\", style: .headlineLarge, color: .primary)","","\/\/ Icons scale proportionally","IronIcon(systemName: \"star\", size: .medium, color: .primary)","","\/\/ Spacing adapts to maintain visual balance","IronButton(\"Submit\", size: .large) { }"]},{"anchor":"ScaledMetric-Usage","text":"ScaledMetric Usage","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Components use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@ScaledMetric"},{"text":" for consistent scaling:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct MyComponent: View {","    @ScaledMetric(relativeTo: .body) private var iconSize: CGFloat = 20","","    var body: some View {","        Image(systemName: \"star\")","            .frame(width: iconSize, height: iconSize)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Testing-Dynamic-Type","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Testing Dynamic Type"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test your interfaces across the full range of sizes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Extra Small","type":"text"}]},{"text":" - Smallest readable size","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Large"}]},{"type":"text","text":" - System default"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"XXX-Large"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" - Large text preference","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accessibility XXX-Large"}]},{"text":" - Maximum accessibility size","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Reduced Motion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Reduced-Motion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"IronUI respects the user’s reduced motion preference.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Automatic Adaptation","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Automatic-Adaptation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Animations automatically simplify when reduced motion is enabled:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Uses spring animation normally, instant transition with reduced motion","IronButton(\"Tap me\") { }","","\/\/ Progress spinner stops animated when reduced motion is on","IronSpinner()"]},{"level":3,"text":"Manual Checking","type":"heading","anchor":"Manual-Checking"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Check the preference manually for custom animations:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct MyView: View {","    @Environment(\\.accessibilityReduceMotion) private var reduceMotion","","    var body: some View {","        content","            .animation(reduceMotion ? nil : .spring(), value: isExpanded)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Accessible-Animation-Modifier","level":3,"text":"Accessible Animation Modifier","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"accessibleAnimation"},{"text":" modifier for automatic handling:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["MyView()","    .accessibleAnimation(.bouncy, value: isExpanded)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"Color and Contrast","type":"heading","anchor":"Color-and-Contrast"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"IronUI’s semantic colors maintain WCAG contrast ratios.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Semantic Colors","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Semantic-Colors"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Always use semantic color tokens:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Good: Semantic colors adapt to context","IronText(\"Error message\", style: .bodyMedium, color: .error)","","\/\/ Avoid: Hardcoded colors may not have sufficient contrast","Text(\"Error\").foregroundColor(.red)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"High-Contrast-Mode","level":3,"text":"High Contrast Mode","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components automatically enhance contrast when the user enables high contrast mode in system settings."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Best-Practices","level":2,"text":"Best Practices","type":"heading"},{"text":"Do","type":"heading","anchor":"Do","level":3},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use descriptive labels that convey purpose","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test with VoiceOver enabled","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Verify layouts at all Dynamic Type sizes","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Respect reduced motion preferences","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use semantic colors for text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Don’t","type":"heading","anchor":"Dont","level":3},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Hide interactive elements from accessibility"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rely solely on color to convey information"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use fixed font sizes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Force animations without checking preferences"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create contrast ratios below 4.5:1"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Testing Accessibility","type":"heading","anchor":"Testing-Accessibility","level":2},{"text":"Xcode Accessibility Inspector","type":"heading","anchor":"Xcode-Accessibility-Inspector","level":3},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Open "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode > Open Developer Tool > Accessibility Inspector"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Select your running simulator"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Inspect elements and verify labels, traits, and values","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"VoiceOver Testing","type":"heading","anchor":"VoiceOver-Testing","level":3},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable VoiceOver in Settings > Accessibility > VoiceOver"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Navigate your app using swipe gestures","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Verify all interactive elements are reachable","type":"text"}]}]},{"content